foia:ProcessedRequestSection.foia:FootnoteText: After reviewing their databases, the following components adjusted the number of requests pending as of the start of the Fiscal Year: CBP, CISA, FEMA, FLETC, FPS I&A, ICE, OIG, PRIV, TSA, USCG, USCIS, and USSS.
